These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, parkour
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | parkour | cricket | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, apricot, pomegranate
1. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | eggplant | pomegranate | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, gardening, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | video-games | gardening | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, blues, salsa
1. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | salsa | blues |

 #################################

 
